#, no-c-format
msgid "Authors"
msgstr "Autors"

#. Tag: para
#: man-rkward.1.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rkward; was written by Thomas Friedrichsmeier and the &rkward; team. See "
"<ulink url=\"https://rkward.kde.org/\">the &rkward; website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"El &rkward; ha estat escrit per en Thomas Friedrichsmeier i l'equip del "
"&rkward;. Vegeu <ulink url=\"https://rkward.kde.org/\">el lloc web del "
"&rkward;</ulink>."
